Lewis Hamilton sprayed champagne in Liu Siying's face after winning Chinese Grand Prix . 
  The 23-year-old was a 'podium girl' at the race in Shanghai on Sunday . 
  Campaigners called his behaviour 'selfish and inconsiderate' but she said she wasn't offended . 
  She said she was told to stand on the podium and was just doing her job . 
  Hamilton has also sprayed a hostess after winning the Spanish Grand Prix and at the Austrian GP . 
  He has been called a 'bully' and 'embarrassment to the UK'